item.title: Contact
item.description: Biomonitoring and biodetection services wilderlab is a New Zealand based company dedicated to the detection and monitoring of rare and invasive species as well as biological water quality evaluation.

item.title: FAQ
item.description: 1. What do you do? We provide environmental DNA biomonitoring services nationally and internationally. 2. Where are you? We are based in Wellington, New Zealand. In case you haven’t found the answer for your question please feel free to contact us, our customer support will be happy to help you.
